{"id":172846,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/08/译者-《译者》每日原文推荐-2011817/","date":"2011-08-18T03:00:21Z","modified":"2011-08-18T03:00:21Z","title":"译者 | 《译者》每日原文推荐 &#8211; 2011/8/17","content":"<p><p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以下为每日原文推荐。如果你有兴趣，请参与翻译并将译文寄给</span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://yyyyiiii.blogspot.com/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《译者》</span></a><b>(</b><span><b><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"mailto:iyizhe@gmail.com\"><span>iyizhe@gmail.com</span></a>)</span></b></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以便与大家共享。欢迎使用</span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feedburner.google.com/fb/a/mailverify?uri=yizhe&#038;loc=en_US\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">邮件组</span></a><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">、</span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://goo.gl/f1NDK\">Google Reader</a><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">和推特（</span><span><span>@yigroup</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，</span></span><span><span>@xiaomi2020</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">）跟踪我们的最新消息。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【时政热点】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《环球邮报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/world/asia-pacific/china-launches-anti-terror-campaign-in-restive-west-region-of-xinjiang/article2131998/?utm_medium=Feeds:+RSS/Atom&#038;utm_source=Asia-Pacific&#038;utm_content=2131998\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国在新疆发起了两个月的</span>“<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">严打</span>”<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">运动</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，针对暴力、恐怖分子和伊斯兰极端分</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">子</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《赫芬顿邮报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2011/08/16/human-rights-groups-biden-china_n_928726.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">人权活动组织敦促副总统拜登访华时关注中国侵犯人权问</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">题</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约时报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2011/08/14/world/asia/14filmmaker.html?_r=1\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国独立导演赵亮的经历</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——从执导《上访》，到受官方影响退出墨尔本电影节，受到艾未未质疑，到与卫生部合作拍《在一起》，这是怎样一个路</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">径</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华尔街日报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blogs.wsj.com/chinarealtime/2011/08/16/china-state-broadcaster-cctvgoes-after-baidu-ad-practices-again/?mod=google_news_blog\">CCTV<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">调查节目再次对准百度</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，指责搜索引擎服务商允许假药贩子做广告，欺骗广告客户付更多的</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">钱</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《卫报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2011/aug/16/chinese-state-media-tax-hoax\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">伪造的国税调整公告骗了中国媒体</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——包括国有媒体。新华社甚至称它曾就该公告采访了国税局官</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">员</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约时报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2011/08/17/world/asia/17trains.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">周二，铁道部宣布其发言人王勇平被免</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">职</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《洛杉矶时报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.latimes.com/business/la-fi-china-economy-20110817,0,1975246.story\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国为</span>08<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">年全球金融危机采取的刺激经济措施导致了通货膨胀</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">；很多建设工程，包括购物商场和办公楼，无人入</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">驻</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span>MSNBC</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/44168426/ns/technology_and_science-space/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国的天宫一号空间站，可能在本月底上天，比人们的预期要</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">快</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华尔街日报》：美国官员希望在拜登访华之行中，</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424053111904253204576512053506646070.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">发现</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国下任领导人习近平的庐山真面</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">目</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约时报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2011/08/17/world/asia/17briefs-Copter.html?_r=1&#038;partner=rssnyt&#038;emc=rss\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国周二否认有关巴基斯坦让中国研究坠毁美军直升飞机的说</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">法</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span>CNN</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://edition.cnn.com/2011/WORLD/europe/08/16/uk.riots.jailed/index.html?eref=rss_world&#038;utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed:+rss/cnn_world+%28RSS:+World%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">周二，英国警方宣布，两位男子因通过社交网站煽动骚乱，被判处</span>4<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">年徒</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">刑</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《环球邮报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/world/asia-pacific/afghan-cleaner-shot-and-killed-inside-nato-headquarters/article2131142/?utm_medium=Feeds:+RSS/Atom&#038;utm_source=Asia-Pacific&#038;utm_content=2131142\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">一名男性阿富汗清洁工在北约总部内被枪杀身亡</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。联军说调查正在进行。联合国数据显示，</span></span><span><span>2011</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">年上半年阿富汗因战争死亡平民</span></span><span><span>1462</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">人，比</span></span><span><span>2010</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">年增长</span></span><span><span>15%</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，</span></span><span><span>80%</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">死于空袭</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《路透社》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/08/17/us-india-protest-idUSTRE77G0PF20110817\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">印度逮捕反腐败活动家哈扎尔，导致其支持者们在各地抗议</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。辛格总理认为哈扎尔用绝食的方式来逼迫国会通过草案，完全是错误</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【经济金融】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华尔街日报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blogs.wsj.com/chinarealtime/2011/08/17/china-yuan-strength-doesnt-necessarily-extend-beyond-dollar/?mod=WSJBlog\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">人民币对美元屡创新高</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，然而由于欧元对美元升值得更快，人民币对欧元实际上还在贬</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">值</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华尔街日报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blogs.wsj.com/chinarealtime/2011/08/17/venture-capital-survey-china-is-a-land-of-bountiful-opportunity/?mod=WSJBlog\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">一份对投资公司的调查发现，</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国充满机会</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——</span></span><span><span>37.7%</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">认为在中国的风险投资将大幅增加，</span></span><span><span>49.1%</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">认为将稍稍增</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">加</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【生活百态】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《外交政策》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.foreignpolicy.com/articles/2011/08/15/huge_in_asia?page=0,0\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">在亚洲（中国）搞大的美国品牌</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——别克、蓝带</span></span><span><span>1844</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">、</span></span><span><span>KFC</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">、花花公子和卡卡圈（泰国</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">）</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<div><i>友情提示：译者Podcast已登录iTunes，到<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://itunes.apple.com/us/podcast/id453722327?ign-mpt=uo%3D4\">这里</a>即可收听往期的译者音频节目；需翻墙更新下载。</i><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5425822223623422432-2115810748264155515?l=yyyyiiii.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=738338\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"738338\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":540,"categories":[1],"tags":[18843]}